{"tid":2359844,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果App Store去年營收料大增28% 超過640億美元","createTime":"2021-01-09T08:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T09:15:04.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07dd0c67bfdfd72c7c55e645b5336b4d61bf245f","tid":2359844,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2848271/APPSTORE_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2848271%2FAPPSTORE_1024.jpg&h=e90adffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果（美：AAPL）應用商店App Store受惠疫情「宅」經濟，<span class=\"red\">CNBC分析估算，App Store在2020年的營收超過640億美元（約4,990億港元）</span>，而2019年、2018年的估計數據分別500億、485億美元，意味App Store去年營收加速增長，升幅由2019年的3.1%大幅加快至28%。<br />\n<br />\nApp Store為蘋果的核心增長業務，歸入蘋果的服務收入分部，該業務分部在截至去年9月底的財年錄得收入537億美元。但豐厚的利潤也為蘋果招致批評，有指App Store擁有太大權力，目前App Store會抽取3成佣金。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果對小型開發者抽成改為15%<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院司法機構反壟斷小組委員會認為，蘋果APP Store對開發者有著絕對壟斷的權力，令蘋果可以獲得巨額利潤。蘋果目前也正被美國遊戲廠商Epic Games起訴，認為蘋果30%的抽成並不公平。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果否認App Store具壟斷權力，但公司近期修改其費用結構，對於App Store收入在100萬美元以下的開發者，僅會抽取15%收入，而非30%。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果一般不會披露其通過App Store獲得的收入，但自2013年以來，蘋果會公佈公司從2008年至今向開發者支付的累計金額，蘋果在周三公佈自2008年共向開發者支付2000億美元，亦即2020年支付的金額為450億美元，按照開發商佔7成營收粗略計算，意味蘋果App Store去年收入超過640億美元。"},{"pid":"fb252460469e064443b0715097666a63b4e716af","tid":2359844,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"股價反映唔到營收 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cd141d1628a1db0093571d63275c6158942202","tid":2359844,"uid":224560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fb252460469e064443b0715097666a63b4e716af","tid":2359844,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"股價反映唔到營收 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"股價剩係識磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3719a31aacd4e4fda38a99b24d325244386fae2","tid":2359844,"uid":99243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"武肺受益人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b927ba0557ec4ac31681ecdbd7e7809c17d5f6f","tid":2359844,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb252460469e064443b0715097666a63b4e716af","tid":2359844,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"股價反映唔到營收 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2022年 蘋果應該會突破140大關"},{"pid":"24a24e4f53a269449ffe0f5b9ccd2d090741f06c","tid":2359844,"uid":185872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83cf63b5e0501c75edb8bf34491aaf4970157f5","tid":2359844,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24a24e4f53a269449ffe0f5b9ccd2d090741f06c","tid":2359844,"uid":185872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"2020report-2019report=2019金額<br />\n2020金額/0.7=64.2 B"}]}